<HEADLINE> Team Standings at World Junior Ice Hockey Championship </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Following are the team
standings at the World Junior Ice Hockey Championship (tabulated
under matches played, won, drawn, lost, goals for, against and
points):
</P>
<P>
Group A:
</P>
<P>
Czech Republic 4 2 2 0 12 7 6
</P>
<P>
Canada 4 2 2 0 9 5 6
</P>
<P>
United States  4 1 2 1 5 6 4
</P>
<P>
Finland  4 1 1 2 8 9 3
</P>
<P>
Slovak 4 0 1 3 4 11 1
</P>
<P>
Group B:
</P>
<P>
Russia 4 4 0 0 30 4 8
</P>
<P>
