<HEADLINE> People's Daily Publishes New Year Message (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 31 (Xinhua) -- China will hold high the great
banner of Marxism and Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought and Deng
Xiaoping Theory, rally round the Party Central Committee with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core, work hard with one heart and one
mind, deepen reform and promote development so as to create a
still more splendid future in the new century.
</P>
<P>
In its New Year's message titled "Greeting the Dawn of the New
Century," the People's Daily, China's leading newspaper, says this
practice in the past year and in the past decade as well has
eloquently proven that the basic line and principles of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) have been shown correct at a time
when the country is confronted with complicated domestic and
international situations.
</P>
<P>
The 20th century is approaching its end, the message says. The
achievements of civilization created by mankind in the past 2,000
years and the dear price paid for them inspired the Chinese people
to firmly explore into the future.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese nation, which has one fifth of the world's
population, created a brilliant ancient civilization and is now
building socialism with Chinese characteristics, shoulders the
heavy responsibility of creating new developments in the new
century.
</P>
<P>
From the middle of the last century to the middle of this one,
the Chinese people finally achieved national independence and
people's liberation after 100 years of bloody struggles, the
message says. And from the middle of this century to the middle of
next century, the Chinese nation will basically achieve socialist
modernization and will stand proud among the family of nations.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, the message recalls that the Chinese people have,
under the leadership of the Communist Party of China (CPC),
undergone untold sufferings and severe tests in the past centuries.
</P>
<P>
As bells chime in celebration of the coming new millennium, the
Chinese people are overjoyed with the advancement of mankind
during the past 1,000 years.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese people also are proud of their glorious
achievements made in the past, the newspaper says.
</P>
<P>
It stresses that 1999 is an important year for the Chinese
people in terms of its battles against various difficulties.
</P>
<P>
Under complex internal and international conditions, China hit
goals in the process of reform and opening and the economic
development.
</P>
</TEXT>
