<HEADLINE> Millennium Countdown Parties Kick off in Singapore </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, December 31 (Xinhua)-- An awesome motorcade of about
170 motorbikes kicked off on Friday Singapore's biggest countdown
street party, the Millennium Swing Singapore, with a roaring start.
</P>
<P>
For the night, Ochard Road, the central shopping palace which
at a normal date would be bustling with streaming vehicles, saw
more than 500,000 revelers swinging at the accompany of pounding
music and dazzling laser shows.
</P>
