the national police, to monitor indiscriminate firing and acts
inimical to public safety during the New Year's eve revelry.
</P>
<P>
The NCRPO has also formed a reports center on illegal discharge
of firearms by policemen and other gun holders, Bucayu said.
</P>
<P>
According to Bucayu, the NCRPO will similarly monitor any
incident that may occur related to the Y2K millennium bug.
