of the whole country. At the 50th Anniversary of the founding of
the People's Republic of China, our motherland displayed her
remarkable achievements in industry, agriculture, education and
national defense. A few weeks ago, the "Shenzhou" spacecraft was
launched successfully into outer space. China is likely to join
the World Trade Organization soon. All these developments
demonstrate that our country is thriving and that the Chinese
people are making steady progress on all fronts," Tung added.
</P>
