southern Afghanistan that Indian Foreign Minister Jaswant Singh is
expected to arrive in Kandahar at 0930 GMT, said reports reaching
here from Kandahar.
</P>
<P>
The Indian Airlines plane, Airbus-300, with more than 150
people on board, has remained stranded at the Kandahar airport for
the seventh day.
</P>
