<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Former South African
President Nelson Mandela, who has come to symbolize South Africa's
victory over racism and oppression, on Friday lit a symbolic flame
of hope for the new millennium in his former prison cell on Robben
Island.
</P>
