<HEADLINE> President Clinton Kicks Off America's Millennium </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Speaking to several thousand people on the Washington Mall,
Clinton called the turn of the millennium "a unique moment" for
the country, coming at a time when the economy is strong and
people are trying to resolve lingering social problems.
</P>
<P>
"There is no better moment to reflect on our hopes and dreams
and the gifts we want to leave our children; no better opportunity
