unveiled a prototype for a time capsule that will be filled with
artifacts symbolic of life in the 20th century and Americans'
hopes and dreams for the nation's future.
</P>
<P>
Once filled, the time capsule, made out of three different
metals and shaped in a flag form, will be sealed and kept at the
National Archives to be opened in 100 years. 
